  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hylia.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You summon forth a jutsu of divine strength by bringing out the full power of your seal of fate. You begin to generate a prismatic aura of light and your eyes shift to a golden yellow for but a moment. You raise your hand in front of you with the back of your palm towards a creature within range that you can see. The creature must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a success, this jutsu fails.</p><p>On a failed save, the seal in your hand manifests physically and surrounds the creature, restraining and incapacitating them for the duration of this jutsu. You then teleport to the creature with incredible speed and make a number of melee attacks equal to your proficiency bonus in the blink of an eye. You can choose for these attacks to be ninjutsu (you strike the enemy with bursts of radiant energy) or taijutsu attacks (you strike the enemy with your fists or a weapon) at casting. On each hit, you deal 2d6 force damage.</p><p>If 5 or more of your attacks hit, you make one final melee attack, of the same type as the previous attacks, dazing the creature and knocking them back 60 feet + an additional 5 feet for every attack that was successful. This jutsu then ends.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
